      <title>从中国到特斯拉：本周末伦敦抗议指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-15/thousands-of-protesters-expected-to-gather-in-london-amid-police-warnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计成千上万的抗议者将在周六聚集在伦敦，因为大都会警察在三个单独的示威活动中施加了条件。]]></description>
